long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Linkhouse SEO Backlink Finder - Your ease in searching for links


Our plugin allows you to directly find sources in Google search results from which you can obtain valuable links.


Linkhouse SEO Backlink Finder is a free extension available for the Google Chrome browser, which simplifies the discovery of places to publish while using the search engine on a daily basis.


Information about links is presented clearly without disrupting the clarity of the search results. 

From within Google search results, you'll get to know:
The lowest publication price on a given website,
The SEO factors of the website and some metrics created by us,
The level of article indexing.


Using the plugin, you will find websites ready to publish your content. Directly from the search engine, you can:
Access the offer of a particular website with a single click,
Add selected domains to a list, and then conveniently check all the added websites,
Use a filter that will only show you websites ready to accept your content, along with their rankings, or those that currently aren't publishing content.


With the Linkhouse SEO Backlink Finder plugin, without the need for additional tools, you will get to know the most important information that will help you choose the right places for publication.
